{"tid":1069981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷鋒周末襲港 料狂風雷暴驟雨跌8度 周日17°C","createTime":"2019-03-20T10:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T13:29:06.000Z","uid":53379,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3844dacdfb4faec9bfaf88e6788e47d28c669a","tid":1069981,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冷鋒周末襲港 料狂風雷暴驟雨跌8度 周日17&deg;C</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190319/large/1552987787_9a83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190319%2Flarge%2F1552987787_9a83.png&h=8ff0997e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暖的海洋氣流正影響廣東沿岸，本港今（20日）明兩日有霧，部份時間有陽光，惟天氣在後日的周五漸轉不穩定。天文台預計，冷鋒會在後日中午後橫過華南沿岸，本港屆時將「有驟雨及局部地區狂風雷暴」，離岸海域間中吹強風，周六中午前局部地區仍有狂風雷暴，全日「多雲有雨」。<br />\n<br />\n氣溫方面，市區氣溫今明兩日仍會高見27&deg;C，惟現時支配本港的溫暖海洋氣流，至本周後期將被東北季候風取代，本港周末顯著轉涼；市區氣溫由周五最高的26&deg;C，跌至周六最低的18&deg;C，周日進一步下試17&deg;C的清涼水平，隨後數天因季候風緩和，氣溫才回升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190320/59385523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59385523&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9PDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=91846245\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59385523&h=cbb96138\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190320/59385523</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ee127ee01b4ff4d6e2a2439ec16467584bfb04","tid":1069981,"uid":42090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T10:25:10.000Z","msg":"又真係幾大乳"},{"pid":"877311428efe4fca7a9847c28f67b0e3763a0147","tid":1069981,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score